15 them in achieving their personal goals and creating a more viable and sustainable agriculture
16 industry in Georgia; and
17 WHEREAS, it is abundantly fitting and proper that the outstanding accomplishments of this
18 extraordinary organization be appropriately recognized.
19 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE SENATE that the members of this body
20 commend the Georgia Young Farmer Teacher Program and extend best wishes for future
21 growth and success.
22 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Secretary of the Senate is authorized and directed
23 to make an appropriate copy of this resolution available for distribution to the Georgia Young
24 Farmer Teacher Program.
